// Features:
// â€¢ Customizable confidence scoring with adjustable component weights
// â€¢ Multi-timeframe analysis for comprehensive market view
// â€¢ Advanced risk management with ATR-based stop-loss and take-profit
// â€¢ Enhanced alerts with detailed ticker and timeframe information
// â€¢ Color-coded background shading for buy/sell zones
